    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. u mentioned the costs for compliance, but i'm hearing a lot from local business owners that these mandates are basically impossible for smaller shops to absorb without closing down. is there any data on whether the \"innovation\" and \"efficiency\" benefits actually happen in real time, or is that more of a theoretical thing?",
